{"word":"παραισθάνομαι","slug":"παραισθάνομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>παραισθάνομαι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-αισθήσομαι</el>) (aor2 <el>-ῃσθόμην</el>) </el><p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a>:— <i>to remark</i> or <i>hear of by the way</i>, <el>τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <el>οὐχὶ παρῄσθευ</el> <i>(doric for</i> <el>παρῄσθου</el>), <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/>"}]}